✨Today I turn 41✨ This year around the moon has been one of the toughest rides I’ve had, but the growth has been amazing Thank you everyone for all the Bday wishes✨✨ I know I’m not one to get sappy on here, but thank you to those who stood close to me, you know who you are! Also big shout out to my therapist! This week marks a year!!! Never knew how much I needed it and I’m proud of the work I’ve done. Anyone going thru it please don’t be too proud to see someone- Once again thank you all and can’t wait to see what the next year has in store for me ✌️ #virgoseason
